OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FVariable amounts of cloud with a good
OL,7,Fdeal of dry weather but a few showers
OL,8,Fnot to be ruled out. Becoming often
OL,9,Fwarm or very warm in sunny intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
